HEADWORD: Metonymical
<hw>Met`o*nym"ic*al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Metonymy</er>.]</ety>
<def>Used by way of metonymy; using the name of one thing for that of
another with which it is closely associated.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Met`o*nym"ic*al*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

